      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of October 19 World Briefing article on an Italian constitutional amendment that allows citizens living abroad to elect their own legislators</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, a report in the World Briefing column on Thursday about an Italian constitutional amendment that allows citizens living abroad to elect their own legislators referred incorrectly in some copies to the voting method. Absentee balloting is not allowed.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Because of an editing error, a report in the World Briefing column on Thursday about an Italian constitutional amendment that allows citizens living abroad to elect their own legislators referred incorrectly in some copies to the voting method. Absentee balloting is not allowed.</p>
